      A ResultSet which wraps another ResultSet, providing an MaterializedOrderedResultSet.iterator() method which returns objects from the wrapped ResultSet in sorted order according to a comparator supplied to the constructor of this ResultSet, AND which implicitly deduplicates the objects returned as well.
